import React from "react" function Buttons(props){ const btnNoviFilm = props.state.roles.includes("ROLE_ADMIN") && const btnSviKorisnici = props.state.roles.includes("ROLE_ADMIN") && const btnLogout = props.state.logdeUsername !== "" && const btnProjekcije = props.state.logdeUsername !== "" && const btnNovaProjekcija = props.state.roles.includes("ROLE_ADMIN") && return(
{btnNoviFilm} {btnSviKorisnici} {btnNovaProjekcija}
) } export default Buttons
